        <title type="html"><![CDATA[在ubuntu中搭建node环境]]></title>
        <id>https://ihzurgnauh.github.io/notes/in-ubuntu-setting-node-environment</id>
        <link href="https://ihzurgnauh.github.io/notes/in-ubuntu-setting-node-environment"/>
        <updated>2024-06-12T08:41:33.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>[[toc]]</p>
<h2>1.安装nvm</h2>
<p>为了后面可以方便的使用多个node版本，这里使用nvm<a href="%5Bnvm%5D(https://github.com/nvm-sh/nvm)%E6%98%AFnode.js%E7%9A%84%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8%EF%BC%8C%E6%97%A8%E5%9C%A8%E6%8C%89%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E6%8C%89shell%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%E7%AE%80%E8%80%8C%E8%A8%80%E4%B9%8B%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86node.js%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E3%80%82">^1</a>来进行版本管理</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash">curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash 
</code></pre>
<p>使配置生效，具体的配置文件就按照所使用的shell，这里使用了<a href="https://www.zsh.org/">zsh</a></p>
<pre><code class="language-bash">source ~/.zshrc  
</code></pre>
<p>验证nvm安装情况</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash">nvm -v
</code></pre>
<h2>2.安装node.js</h2>
<p>列出node可用版本</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash">nvm ls-remote  
</code></pre>
<p>可根据所列出的版本来选择安装，这里安装18.20.3</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash">nvm install 18.20.3 
</code></pre>
<h2>3.更换npm源</h2>
<p>更换npm为国内源</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash">npm config set registry https://registry.npmmirror.com 
</code></pre>
<h2>4.使用npm安装pnpm</h2>
<pre><code class="language-bash">npm install -g pnpm 
</code></pre>
]]></content>
